      "review_summary": "The PR adds iMessage outbound allowlist checks for normal sends, private-API send actions, and reply delivery while forwarding trusted requester sender context through shared channel send paths.\n\nPR surface: Source +318, Tests +918. Total +1236 across 14 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source inspection: current main sends through sendMessageIMessage and private send actions without an outbound allowlist gate before transport. I did not run a live iMessage account path in this read-only review.",
